    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can you try using:\n\n``` js\n    search.templatesConfig.helpers.button = function(text){\n        console.log(this); // this should be the entire item\n    };\n```\n\nI am unsure objects are supported. Maybe also try:\n\n``` js\n    search.templatesConfig.helpers.button = function(text, render){\n        console.log(render(text));\n    };\n```\n\nhttps://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#helpers\n\nlet me know\n",
